  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Line <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"l\"></span></span> in the <span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic \">xy</span></span>-plane is perpendicular to the line with equation <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 2\"></span></span>. What is the slope of line <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"l\"></span></span>?</p>\n",
