      "content": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph \">The slope of line <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"l\"></span></span> is undefined.</p>\n"
